    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, well-maintained condition and has served as a reliable daily driver. The exterior paint still holds a great shine, though upon close inspection, you will find some minor stone chips on the hood and a few light surface scratches consistent with its age. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable; the upholstery shows some light wear on the driver's side bolster, but there are no tears or unpleasant odors. Mechanically, the car is sound, with all features functioning as intended and a consistent service history. It is a dependable, honest vehicle that is ready for its next owner.",
